%% Reviewed 2026-04-17 for B-096, CB-122, CB-123, and v0.1.11 to show the proposition-first visible intervention value engine and proposition-native voice composition replacing the block-first signal-ranker and moment-kind phrase-bank paths: evidence intake -> proposition ledger -> hard gates -> value features -> conflict graph and subset optimizer -> visibility broker -> ruled renderer -> Compass decision log and adjudication report.
flowchart LR
    User["Live conversation turn<br/>prompt + assistant summary + edit or bash checkpoint"] --> Hosts
    Packet["Grounded packet + delivery truth<br/>context packet summary + active refs + lane context"] --> Alignment
    RuntimeTruth["Execution + memory + Tribunal truth<br/>execution snapshot + session stream + adjudication signals"] --> Alignment
    History["Governed source truth<br/>Radar + Registry + Atlas + Casebook"] --> Core
    Stream["Compass stream history<br/>dedupe + pending proposal lifecycle"] --> Alignment
    Stream --> Core
    Alignment["alignment_context hot path<br/>compact Context packet + Execution summary<br/>session memory + delivery ledger + Tribunal summary<br/>no provider calls or repo-wide search"] --> Envelope

    subgraph Hosts["Host adapters"]
        Codex["Codex hooks<br/>prompt context + stop summary<br/>Bash post-tool checkpoint"]
        Claude["Claude hooks<br/>prompt context + prompt teaser<br/>stop + post-edit + post-bash checkpoint"]
    end

    Codex --> Envelope["ObservationEnvelope<br/>host_family + session_id + turn_phase<br/>prompt_excerpt + assistant_summary<br/>changed_paths + packet/context summary<br/>execution + memory + Tribunal + visibility summaries<br/>delivery_snapshot + active_target_refs"]
    Claude --> Envelope

    Envelope --> Intake["Evidence intake<br/>Context packet + Execution snapshot<br/>memory/session stream + Tribunal summary<br/>Casebook/Radar/Registry/Atlas anchors<br/>host delivery ledger"]

    subgraph Facts["Fact classes"]
        HistoryFact["history"]
        GovernanceTruth["governance_truth"]
        Invariant["invariant"]
        Topology["topology"]
        Opportunity["capture_opportunity"]
    end

    Intake --> HistoryFact
    Intake --> GovernanceTruth
    Intake --> Invariant
    Intake --> Topology
    Intake --> Opportunity
    Intake --> Propositions["SignalProposition ledger<br/>claim text + support state<br/>anchors + semantic signature<br/>duplicate key + evidence fingerprints"]
    Propositions --> HardGates["Hard gates<br/>unsupported/stale/contradictory<br/>generated-only + hidden-only<br/>duplicate semantic proposition<br/>proposal restatement"]
    HardGates --> Features["InterventionValueFeatures<br/>correctness x positive value<br/>materiality + actionability + novelty<br/>timing + user need + visibility need<br/>minus interruption + redundancy + uncertainty + brand risk"]
    Features --> ConflictGraph["Conflict graph + subset optimizer<br/>top 12 candidates<br/>max 3 ambient + one Observation + one Proposal<br/>hard cap 4 live blocks, Assist excluded"]
    ConflictGraph --> Core["VisibleSignalSelectionDecision<br/>selected + suppressed propositions<br/>utility summary + no-output reason<br/>decision-log payload"]

    Core --> Teaser["Teaser only<br/>one sentence on prompt submit when one strong signal exists"]
    Core --> Ambient["Odylith Risks / History / Insight<br/>multiple only when distinct, supported, high value<br/>zero duplicate propositions"]
    Core --> Observation["**Odylith Observation**<br/>one short human line<br/>the non-obvious fact that changes the next move"]
    Core --> Proposal["**Odylith Proposal**<br/>only when it adds concrete action<br/>one confirmation for the whole bundle"]
    Core --> Broker["VisibleInterventionDecision broker<br/>one shared visibility decision<br/>visible_markdown + developer_context<br/>delivery_channel + delivery_status<br/>proof_required + latency + fingerprints"]

    Teaser --> Broker
    Ambient --> Broker
    Observation --> Broker
    Proposal --> Broker
    Broker --> Events["Compass lifecycle events<br/>intervention_teaser<br/>ambient_signal<br/>intervention_card<br/>capture_proposed<br/>capture_applied<br/>capture_declined<br/>assist_closeout"]
    Broker --> DeliveryMetadata["Delivery metadata<br/>assistant_render_required<br/>assistant_fallback_ready<br/>manual_visible<br/>best_effort_visible<br/>stop_continuation_ready<br/>assistant_chat_confirmed"]

    Broker --> Renderer["Ruled live renderer<br/>repair missing top/bottom rulers<br/>never drop a good signal for ruler absence<br/>Assist remains closeout-owned"]
    Renderer --> Chatter["Odylith Chatter + assistant render<br/>friendly + delightful + soulful<br/>simple + clear + accurate + human"]
    Chatter --> HookPayloads["Hook payloads<br/>systemMessage + additionalContext<br/>structured evidence, not visibility proof"]
    HookPayloads --> AssistantFallback["Assistant-render fallback<br/>speak exact Markdown when host hides hooks<br/>hard fail-visible while proof is missing"]
    Chatter --> ManualVisible["visible-intervention CLI<br/>plain Markdown escape hatch"]
    AssistantFallback --> Chat["Chat-visible UX<br/>Observation / Proposal / Assist actually shown"]
    ManualVisible --> Chat
    HookPayloads --> StopGuard["Stop one-shot continuation<br/>recover missed Assist or late Observation"]
    StopGuard --> Chat
    DeliveryMetadata --> Events
    Events --> Ledger["Delivery ledger<br/>Teaser + Ambient + Observation<br/>Proposal + Assist visibility"]
    Ledger --> Status["intervention-status CLI<br/>static readiness + active lanes<br/>unproven vs proven-this-session<br/>exact fallback smoke"]
    Status --> ChatProbe["Status transcript probe<br/>promotes only exact rendered Markdown<br/>to assistant_chat_confirmed"]
    ChatProbe --> Ledger
    Status --> Chat
    Core --> DecisionLog["Compass decision log<br/>selected + suppressed propositions<br/>semantic conflicts + feature values + utility<br/>evidence fingerprints + duplicate groups + proof state"]
    DecisionLog --> Events
    Corpus["Adjudication corpus<br/>bootstrap quality state<br/>synthetic cases do not count for calibration<br/>real transcript density gates for publishable=true"] --> Benchmark
    Broker --> Benchmark["Value/visibility regression harness<br/>Codex + Claude transcript probes<br/>hidden payload is never success<br/>p95 selector latency <= 15 ms"]
    ChatProbe --> Benchmark

    Chat --> Confirm{"User confirms after visible proposal<br/>apply this proposal"}
    Confirm -->|yes| Apply["CLI-first apply<br/>Radar + Registry + Atlas + Casebook<br/>only where a safe helper exists"]
    Confirm -->|no| Decline["Decline only<br/>no governed write"]

    Apply --> Refresh["Selective owned-surface refresh<br/>Radar / Registry / Atlas / Compass"]
    Apply --> Events
    Decline --> Events
    Events --> Pending["Compass pending proposal state<br/>derived from stream, no second truth store"]

    Voice["Voice composition<br/>fixed structural frame<br/>claim + consequence + next step from evidence"] --> Chatter
    Pending --> Lanes["Same product contract across lanes<br/>detached source-local + pinned dogfood + consumer pinned-runtime"]
